{"tid":489191,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"教你如何增加VR AV臨場感","createTime":"2017-12-04T12:19:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-07T15:28:10.000Z","uid":75969,"like":1915,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":119,"replies":[{"pid":"c92933126a2caef215ba2247359707df2849097c","tid":489191,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T12:19:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171204/640_253255ccc25eb5ff2790193d5082fcc1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171204%2F640_253255ccc25eb5ff2790193d5082fcc1.jpg&h=c5184df8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n左邊是VR A片畫面，右邊是現實畫面。翻攝自《nuwton》<br />\n<br />\nVR(Virtual Reality，虛擬實境)技術，近來也讓日本A片廠商廣泛應用，不過觀看時雖然有身歷其境的感覺，但總是少了那麼一點感覺，於是有人就邊看VR A片，邊去做馬殺雞按摩，雖然這樣的體驗讓他超興奮，但是在旁人看來卻是超悲催。<br />\n<br />\n據《nuwton》報導，編輯セブ山介紹一個讓大家觀看VR A片，有超過百倍樂趣的方法，那就是看人妻回春按摩A片的時候，自己也去做馬殺雞按摩，這樣做的話，當虛擬AV女優在幫你塗按摩油的時候，男按摩師也會同步幫你塗按摩油，感受到虛擬現實結合在一起的感覺，讓你興奮度飆高，而當片中是兩位AV女優幫你服務時，你也可以請兩位安摩師現場幫你按摩，體驗決定快感。<br />\n<br />\n不過這個景象在旁人看來可是超悲催，而當按摩結束後拿下VR眼鏡，看到現實兩位男按摩師，且他們用微妙的表情看著你時，立刻就會從虛擬世界回神，剛剛的舒適體驗只不過是虛擬世界而已。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171204/640_97af0725a1b43972618622cd0f6ff509.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171204%2F640_97af0725a1b43972618622cd0f6ff509.jpg&h=10426c35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n看VR A片有超棒的方法。翻攝自《nuwton》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171204/640_e6d6b99c2d1a8d60f8e35b0d0c98ce7c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171204%2F640_e6d6b99c2d1a8d60f8e35b0d0c98ce7c.jpg&h=be9d14c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n就是去按摩店按摩的時候看按摩A片。翻攝自《nuwton》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171204/640_f4b794a4ba4b1c2f6f24fa976a85c01a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171204%2F640_f4b794a4ba4b1c2f6f24fa976a85c01a.jpg&h=054e7912&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n片中是這個樣子。翻攝自《nuwton》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171204/640_7fac74e78cf96bb4d54966cc19c3114b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171204%2F640_7fac74e78cf96bb4d54966cc19c3114b.jpg&h=0f4056db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但是實際上是這樣子。翻攝自《nuwton》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171204/640_88c011d93d84ed19ae2cbedfcdef97de.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171204%2F640_88c011d93d84ed19ae2cbedfcdef97de.jpg&h=662cfcf9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n想要對片中的女優出手。翻攝自《nuwton》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171204/640_867a93b7f90632ec138d2bd6e04196b5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171204%2F640_867a93b7f90632ec138d2bd6e04196b5.jpg&h=79bd7731&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n按摩師會無言的看著你。翻攝自《nuwton》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171204/640_59a1486f4102eefb78be6fe351212d99.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171204%2F640_59a1486f4102eefb78be6fe351212d99.jpg&h=0f526121&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當玩3P對女優出手時，實際上是摸到男按摩師。翻攝自《nuwton》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171204/640_2efed98de8ff19897b8abbca7d9cef63.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171204%2F640_2efed98de8ff19897b8abbca7d9cef63.jpg&h=da848bbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n他就會用這種表情看著你。翻攝自《nuwton》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171204/640_85e37dac7b23f107014d415f235c2243.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171204%2F640_85e37dac7b23f107014d415f235c2243.jpg&h=af0c4baa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當你看完片子。翻攝自《nuwton》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171204/640_4f5881d012296776426ec7fe957dfcc2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171204%2F640_4f5881d012296776426ec7fe957dfcc2.jpg&h=995bbf54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n並且拿下VR眼鏡後...。翻攝自《nuwton》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171204/640_1642fd7fbb2b6d9050837869e5ea3270.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171204%2F640_1642fd7fbb2b6d9050837869e5ea3270.jpg&h=30a46165&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n男按摩師就會用這種表情看著你。翻攝自《nuwton》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/life/realtime/20171204/1253170/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flife%2Frealtime%2F20171204%2F1253170%2F&d=NlbSeFomOcymNKJohLc7o4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=08a4069e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flife%2Frealtime%2F20171204%2F1253170%2F&h=0f5ccb0b\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/life/realtime/20171204/1253170/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n索性去叫雞好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48227d55e5e3f16ecd2e4234866bc39d7e73e400","tid":489191,"uid":96843,"like":954,"dislike":12,"score":942,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T12:28:42.000Z","msg":"男按摩師：#metoo"},{"pid":"effaa2fa4fe1bd851d21ae60240160c6a4b09d2f","tid":489191,"uid":11026,"like":319,"dislike":4,"score":315,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T12:31:15.000Z","msg":"日本仔真係癡撚哂線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <